## YOUR TASK

Create a mapping from variant option values (typically colors) to their best matching image URL.

## OUTPUT FORMAT

Respond with a JSON object where:
- Keys are the variant option values (e.g., "Blue", "Red", "Black")
- Values are the single best matching image URL

Example:
```json
{{
  "Blue": "https://example.com/images/product-blue-main.jpg",
  "Red": "https://example.com/images/product-red-main.jpg"
}}
```

If you cannot confidently match ANY colors to images, return an empty object:
```json
{{}}
```

## IMPORTANT

- Do NOT include colors that don't have a clear image match
- Do NOT guess based on image order or position alone
- Do NOT invent URLs - only use URLs from the available_images list
- It's acceptable to return an empty object if no confident matches exist

